    "designIntent": "L10-MYSTERY-INTRO+4TUNNEL+HARD-PARKINGPRESSURE-2026-06-10 | HARD. Introduces mystery (2 mystery, center). PARKING-SPACE PRESSURE maxed: green front-hold (G10 < 1 truck/belt forces hold) PLUS blue+yellow held in 8-chunks -> all 3 non-red colors clog dock slots; only red flows clean to fire the 4 tunnels. Result: 2-of-3 slots clog in 99% of plays (even smart), teeters at 3-slot deadlock ~51% -> genuinely hard. Relief = fire tunnels -> grind blue/yellow out -> green resurfaces (G22 deep). 4c/16t/dock3/4 tunnels/2 mystery. Levers=Gate+Hold+Mystery+Unknown(tunnel x4)+ParkingPressure(MAX). ~51% smart-fail (Hard).",
